                                <span class="tooltip-text">
                                    <%= achievements[25].description %>
                                </span>
                            </span>
                        </span>.
                    </p>
                    <h2>Second Playthrough</h2>
                    <p class="indent">
                        For your second playthrough choose hardcore difficulty. Again do not forget the weapon kill
                        challenges. For this playthrough find all the notes and documents for
                        <span class="achievement">
