                            target="_blank">Bookworm Text Guide</a> - text guide with images for all files and
                        notes<br>
                        <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2045535533"
                            target="_blank">"Goodbye, Charlie!" Achievement Guide</a> - text guide with images for all
                        charlie dolls locations<br>
                        <a href="https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=2046764973" target="_blank">100%
                            Achievements Guide</a> - also includes video link for collectibes
                    </p>
